Solo Leveling Arise OVERDRIVE Gameplay Preview - SHOULD You PLAY It? Is It Worth it? (New ARPG)
In this video, we're going to be taking a look at Solo Leveling Arise Overdrive, an upcoming action RPG game being developed by Netmarble and based on the Webtoon with over 14 billion views worldwide. Solo Leveling, the game, was first announced back in June during the Xbox Game Showcase, and now has a proper release date set for November 17th.

Get the game here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2373990/Solo_Leveling_ARISE_OVERDRIVE/
Sponsored by: Solo Leveling Arise Overdrive
